All Implemented Interfaces:
NativeJdbcExtractor
public class P6spyNativeJdbcExtractor
extends SimpleNativeJdbcExtractor

NativeJdbcExtractor for P6Spy - It is referenced from the Spring Data Project's (JDBC Extensions - spring-data-jdbc-core) org.springframework.data.jdbc.support.nativejdbc.P6spyNativeJdbcExtractor We changed it to extend SimpleNativeJdbcExtractor which can set flags(default is false!) for isNativeConnectionNecessaryForXXX methods.

Implementation of the NativeJdbcExtractor interface.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Thomas Risberg, Byunghun Woo
